{"tid":217921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(goal！)20歲咸濕男「胸襲」親母　遭掌摑直接送警","createTime":"2017-04-26T06:51:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T07:11:24.000Z","uid":3514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"035a1a2af62f64dd23e441cdd774e413e2163148","tid":217921,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:51:24.000Z","msg":"台灣新北一名20歲男子，自前年不時趁媽媽不注意時就進行「胸襲」，媽媽極為憤怒多次掌摑，但這名兒子還是不罷休，去年6月媽媽在駛電單車時再下手，母親大義滅親直接將他載到警署提告，檢方昨將這名兒子起訴。<br />\n<br />\n起訴書指出，母親年約50歲，而這名兒子平時不是同住，只是偶而到母親住所探望，但這兒子卻不時偷摸母親胸部，雖然母親曾要他看心理醫生，警告他不要再犯，但他拒絕看病，堅持自己沒有問題。<br />\n<br />\n兒子否認犯案，但檢察官發現除胸襲情節外，全部情節的供詞都一樣，而媽媽沒理由誣告親生子，決定起訴。"},{"pid":"6a08229b97f309a470a77dbf740633f961ac848d","tid":217921,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:51:42.000Z","msg":"source：<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170426/1/10/4/20%E6%AD%B2%E5%92%B8%E6%BF%95%E7%94%B7-%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B2-%E8%A6%AA%E6%AF%8D-%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%91%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%80%81%E8%AD%A6-7308564.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170426%2F1%2F10%2F4%2F20%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2592%25B8%25E6%25BF%2595%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E8%2583%25B8%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%258C%25E6%2591%2591%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6-7308564.html&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=fb00ed8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170426/1/10/4/20%E6%AD%B2%E5%92%B8%E6%BF%95%E7%94%B7-%E8%83%B8%E8%A5%B2-%E8%A6%AA%E6%AF%8D-%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%8C%E6%91%91%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%80%81%E8%AD%A6-7308564.html</a>"},{"pid":"98050af4b6dd188d98277d87b0161976311a3654","tid":217921,"uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"最美麗的風景"},{"pid":"5d498477b8defefbaa76e5e1fe14ae44505410d5","tid":217921,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-2